07. Dionyus
“An Ancient Greek God of wine, ritual madness, fertility, theater. Also referred to as Bacchu, his Roman name. He...
body:
07. Dionyus


“An Ancient Greek God of wine, ritual madness, fertility, theater. Also referred to as Bacchu, his Roman name. He died a tragic death because of Hera’s jealously and had titans attack him, but his father Zeus brought him back to life and gave him his upmost protection. As the “twice-born” god, Dionysus had crossed the boundary between life and death, and he was often portrayed as the god who crossed the boundary between the civilized and uncivilized and the known and unknown. He was represented as a god of chaos and the protector of misfits.”

Dionysus was raised with his identity hidden from Hera so he was raised disguised as a girl. This explains the feminine concepts we are seeing for this comeback. The pearls, the jewelry, the bags, the clothing, all of it ties together. One of the symbols that represents Dionyus is a snake and you can see that Taehyung is wearing a snake bracelet in one of the concept photos.

summary: The bad obsession ff Taehyung chapter 2
title: The bad obsession ff Taehyung chapter 2
body:
Chapter 2

She saw that she had visitors that wasn’t supposed to be there trying to break in her house looking for her.

She took her gun out from under her skirt, and hid behind the bush so she can decide away she wanted to attack them.

“Who the fuck are theses fuckers that thinks they can try to get into my house like this? Where the hell are my bodyguards?” * she said in a very low angry voice so they wouldn’t hear her*

She got out of the bush and started crawling so they wouldn’t see her, even though it’s already dark outside.

When she got close to the, she heard what they was talking about

“We need to find her or our boss will get mad at us. So hurry up and get us in there.” Guy 1 said to the others in a stern voice.

“Shut the fuck up man, do you truly think we haven’t been trying? This girl has six locks on her big ass door.” guy 3 said out of frustration.

“You know what? Since you have your head so far up your ass by making us do all the work, than you take a shot.” Guy 3 said in a threatening tone.

“Fine I will sucker.” *first guy said in a cold tone*

Y/N thoughts: okay here is my cue to start fighting

Time skip to after fighting the guys off

After I killed them I looked through their pants to find information and anything valuable enough to keep for myself. She laughs with an evil smirk on her face.

Haha stupid assholes really thought they would get away with that shit. No one gets by with that crap when it comes to me. She started collecting their money and weapons and information before clearing her regards to clean up the mess so no one finds out.

I walked in my house and while the maids bowed to me out of respect because since i’m a very powerful gangster in Korea and also out of states to. So basically everyone is scared of me. I laughed at that thought and shook my head with amused look on my face.

She went to her office upstairs to her hidden in a secret place behind a bookshelf that no one knew about.

She set at her desk and called her brother ring ring Jiyong answered in less than a minute.

“Hello my handsome brother I need you do something for me.”

“Okay sis what do you need?” my brother Jiyong asked me.

“I need you to look up these four guys I just killed, and see who they are connected with for me.” I said in a serious voice.

“Okay sis, what is their names?” He asked me.

“One is named Beom-seok, two is Hyun-wook, and three is Chan-woo, and four is Hyun-seung.” I told him what their names are.

“Okay sis I’ll search them for you, and then I’ll call you with information.” He informed me.

“Okay bye love you.” I said to my brother.

“Bye love you too sis.” My brother Jiyong said to me before ending the call.

Call ended

Okay time to start getting ready to go clubbing* she jumped with excitement*

She took a shower and did her day routine and makeup done, now what to wear. * she said with a smirk on her face*

I’ll wear this sexy tight dress and these sexy high heels.

I grabbed my bag and car keys than I walked to my garage to pick my car.

And drove off to the club.

When I got in the club after giving my bodyguards my car keys to park it in a safe place due to it being very expensive and has all my guns and knives in it.

Soon as I walked in everyone was looking at me with so much fear in their eyes because they know that I am the most biggest gangster in korea and America.

Hey everyone lets get this party going* she took a shot while everyone did the same and went on with there own business.

She went to the dance floor and started looking for her target. While waiting for her brother to come and meet her with the information she asked him for.

She saw her target TAEYEON, my enemy that I want to kill so bad right now. But I’ll wait for to come to me. * she laughed with an evil smirk on her face*

The second I looked away from her, I saw my brother gave me the sign to follow him, so I did.

We ended up walking up the stairs into a hallway going into a secret VIp room to discuss what I asked him to do for me.

“Okay sis, I found what gang they are from.” He told me.

“Get to the point please brother.” I said to him.

“They are from forceknox, the same as TAEYEON is from.” Jiyong stated to me.

“So is she the last one left in that gang?” I asked my bother.

“Yes surprisingly she is the last one. Why?” Jiyong asked his little sister feeling like something is going to go down.

“Because I am going to end her life now. That bitch messed with the wrong one here.” I screamed at my brother.

Watch your little life end taeyeon….

End of chapter 2

“We need to find her or our boss will get mad at us. So hurry up and get us in there.” Guy 1 said to the others in a stern voice.

“Shut the fuck up man, do you truly think we haven’t been trying? This girl has six locks on her big ass door.” guy 3 said out of frustration.

“You know what? Since you have your head so far up your ass by making us do all the work, than you take a shot.” Guy 3 said in a threatening tone.

“Fine I will sucker.” *first guy said in a cold tone*

Y/N thoughts: okay here is my cue to start fighting

Time skip to after fighting the guys off

After I killed them I looked through their pants to find information and anything valuable enough to keep for myself. She laughs with an evil smirk on her face.

Haha stupid assholes really thought they would get away with that shit. No one gets by with that crap when it comes to me. She started collecting their money and weapons and information before clearing her regards to clean up the mess so no one finds out.

I walked in my house and while the maids bowed to me out of respect because since i’m a very powerful gangster in Korea and also out of states to. So basically everyone is scared of me. I laughed at that thought and shook my head with amused look on my face.

She went to her office upstairs to her hidden in a secret place behind a bookshelf that no one knew about.

She set at her desk and called her brother ring ring Jiyong answered in less than a minute.

“Hello my handsome brother I need you do something for me.”

“Okay sis what do you need?” my brother Jiyong asked me.

“I need you to look up these four guys I just killed, and see who they are connected with for me.” I said in a serious voice.

“Okay sis, what is their names?” He asked me.

“One is named Beom-seok, two is Hyun-wook, and three is Chan-woo, and four is Hyun-seung.” I told him what their names are.

“Okay sis I’ll search them for you, and then I’ll call you with information.” He informed me.

“Okay bye love you.” I said to my brother.

“Bye love you too sis.” My brother Jiyong said to me before ending the call.

Call ended

Okay time to start getting ready to go clubbing* she jumped with excitement*

She took a shower and did her day routine and makeup done, now what to wear. * she said with a smirk on her face*

I’ll wear this sexy tight dress and these sexy high heels.

I grabbed my bag and car keys than I walked to my garage to pick my car.

And drove off to the club.

When I got in the club after giving my bodyguards my car keys to park it in a safe place due to it being very expensive and has all my guns and knives in it.

Soon as I walked in everyone was looking at me with so much fear in their eyes because they know that I am the most biggest gangster in korea and America.

Hey everyone lets get this party going* she took a shot while everyone did the same and went on with there own business.

She went to the dance floor and started looking for her target. While waiting for her brother to come and meet her with the information she asked him for.

She saw her target TAEYEON, my enemy that I want to kill so bad right now. But I’ll wait for to come to me. * she laughed with an evil smirk on her face*

The second I looked away from her, I saw my brother gave me the sign to follow him, so I did.

We ended up walking up the stairs into a hallway going into a secret VIp room to discuss what I asked him to do for me.

“Okay sis, I found what gang they are from.” He told me.

“Get to the point please brother.” I said to him.

“They are from forceknox, the same as TAEYEON is from.” Jiyong stated to me.

“So is she the last one left in that gang?” I asked my bother.

“Yes surprisingly she is the last one. Why?” Jiyong asked his little sister feeling like something is going to go down.

“Because I am going to end her life now. That bitch messed with the wrong one here.” I screamed at my brother.

Watch your little life end taeyeon….

End of chapter 2
